    {
        "content": "<p>frau opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13591\">PR #13591</a> from <code>frau:memory-swap</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Hot swap an existing Memory backing buffer with another. Requires the new memory to be shaped the same as the old.</p>\n<p>Obviously this won't be safe for the semantics of a wasm module that isn't expecting it, but I'm writing a program which would benefit from hot-swapping specific linear memory banks in and out while retaining the same code module.</p>\n</blockquote>",
